{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c2a3b5a37","title":"周恩来关于新疆红二司抄赛福鼎家等问题的指示","origin":"抄自红二司八农兵团《九三烽火》41期68.5.8并参照红二司新大星火燎原兵团《学习参考》68.5.31所载校对","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b977773fec","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"ee21afb82f","name":"新疆文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6518784343","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于新疆红二司抄赛福鼎家等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"ea16fd8b27","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"3fd8abfaa5","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：下午两点三十分〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"7cde392c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"周峰同志传达：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"0fd3aa9fa6","type":"paragraph","text":"总理指示说：红二司这样做是不对的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"d5e548c714","type":"paragraph","text":"运动已搞了两年多了，不能再搞打、砸、抢、抄。红二司是新疆一个主要造反派，把他们放在新疆的文化大革命中的一个重要位置。他们每犯错误，（总理）都及时指出，他们自己也注意改正了，但是不能总犯错误。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"a433753e43","type":"paragraph","text":"拿走的东西都要立即一律交还，今后不能再犯。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"},{"id":"ad149485e8","type":"paragraph","text":" （抄自红二司八农兵团《九三烽火》41期68.5.8并参照红二司新大星火燎原兵团《学习参考》68.5.31所载校对）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37"}],"page":{"id":"70c654a8fd","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4c2a3b5a37","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}